snippet.title: Cafemart Simulator Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3408110/Cafemart_Simulator/

Build, decorate, and manage your very own grocery store, complete with a cozy restaurant where customers can shop and enjoy a delicious meal. Play solo or team up with friends in co-op multiplayer!
